reviewText: This brought back memories of being a kid on Saturday morning. Wish there had been more Heckle & Jeckle cartoons.
My friends asked me for this so I brought it. They love it because it brings back memories for them.
/there was one little H&J cartoon.  It was different voices, from before they became Heckle & Jeckle.  I was disappointed.
simply a wonderful videotape from the age of terrytoons, with the likes of mighty mouse, deputy dawg and of course heckle & jeckle;
